    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-12 text-center">
                <h1 class="display-4 mt-5">Welcome to ZipperMate</h1>
                <p>
                    Welcome to ZipperMate, your one-stop destination
                    for all things zipper-related! We are thrilled to
                    have you here. Whether you're looking for high-quality
                    for your clothing projects, innovative zipper
                    accessories, or expert advice on zipper maintenance,
                    you've come to the right place. At ZipperMate,
                    we take pride in delivering top-notch products and
                    exceptional customer service to ensure your zipping
                    experience is as smooth as can be. Explore our wide
                    range of zipper solutions and discover how we can help
                    you zip up your world. Thank you for choosing ZipperMate,
                    where zippers are our passion!

                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
