                    <img src="/images/metal.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Metal">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text custom-text">At ZipperMate, our unwavering dedication to crafting superior zippers hinges on our meticulous selection of high-grade metals. In the intricate world of fasteners, we understand that metal is the very essence of our product. It is the elemental foundation upon which our zippers are built, dictating not only their functional prowess but also their resilience and trustworthiness.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <img src="/images/strength.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="Strength">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text custom-text">Our commitment to strength and durability is evident in every detail of our zippers. From the choice of robust materials to the precision engineering of our products, we leave no stone unturned in ensuring they can withstand the test of time and wear.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card mb-4">
                    <img src="/images/bag.jpeg" class="card-img-top" alt="...">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="card-text custom-text">ZipperMate zippers are the perfect choice for bags and utility bags, offering unparalleled functionality and reliability. Whether you're using them for everyday carry bags, travel luggage, or specialized utility bags, our zippers are designed to excel in every scenario.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
